Sentencas: Thenanosize(La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9(SDC)composite cathodes were prepared by impregnating high entropy (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (HE-LNSSB) catalytic phase into the SDC electrode skeleton.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: The catalytic activity and the stability of the nano-size LNSSB phase are investigated.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: The XRD results show that the orthorhombic perovskite phase was obtained when the HE-LNSSB precursor was calcined at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: At 700 degrees C, the pristine nano-size HE-LNSSB/SDC composite cathode shows a specific polar resistance (Rasp) of 0.30 Omega.cm2.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: The Rasp of the pristine nano-size HE-LNSSB composite cathode was reduced by 50.8 % compared with that of the sintered HE-LNSSB cathode.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: The Rasp of the aged nano-size HE-LNSSB com-posite cathode was 0.31 Omega.cm2 at 700 degrees C and the catalytic activity did not decay.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: The SEM and the XPS results show that the particle micrograph of the nano-size HE-LNSSB catalytic phase hardly changes and Sr elements do not segregate on the HE-LNSSB phase surface after being aged.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode

Sentencas: The research results show that the nano-size HE-LNSSB/SDC composite cathode will be a potential cathode material for the intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Preparation of a nano-size (La0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Sr0.2Ba0.2)Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ/SDC high-entropy oxide composite cathode
